      "name": "鹿暝"
    },
    {
      "id": "huaiyi",
      "name": "槐姨"
    },
    {
      "id": "folding_artisan",
      "name": "折页匠"
    },
    {
      "id": "guard",
      "name": "卫兵"
    },
    {
      "id": "monitor_voice",
      "name": "监察音"
    },
    {
      "id": "sailor",
      "name": "风帆卫士"
    },
    {
      "id": "umbrella_master",
      "name": "空伞师"
    },
    {
      "id": "prince_li",
      "name": "砾亲王"
    },
    {
      "id": "decoder",
      "name": "译码员"
    },
    {
      "id": "chengan",
      "name": "澄安"
    }
  ],
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "T1_01",
      "title": "拾声王国的清晨",
      "scene": {
        "background": "bg_t1_01",
        "music": "BGM_02_fairytale_morning",
        "transition": "fade"
      },
      "steps": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "text": "拾声王国把每个人的一生都写进铃铛。风一吹，整座城就像在翻一本书。"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "speaker": "luming",
          "text": "父王说，故事能让人记得自己是谁。可昨夜之后，王宫里少了三十九只铃。"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "speaker": "huaiyi",
          "text": "不是铃丢了，是铃的主人不见了。连影子都没留下。"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "text": "远处，新来的宫廷匠人正把一张白纸铺在石板上。"
        }
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "T1_01_choice_1",
          "text": "去看那张白纸",
          "target": "T1_02",
          "effects": [
            {
              "type": "inc",
              "key": "science",
              "by": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "T1_01_choice_2",
          "text": "先清点失踪者名单",
          "target": "T1_03",
          "effects": [
            {
              "type": "inc",
              "key": "trust",
              "by": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "T1_01_choice_3",
          "text": "命令卫队封锁画室",
          "target": "T1_04",
          "effects": [
            {
              "type": "inc",
              "key": "risk",
              "by": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "inc",
              "key": "heat",
              "by": 1
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "T1_02",
      "title": "白纸不会平躺",
      "scene": {
        "background": "bg_t1_02",
        "music": "BGM_03_tension_strings",
        "transition": "fade"
      },
      "steps": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "speaker": "folding_artisan",
          "text": "殿下，纸不愿意变平，是因为世界本来不该只有一面。"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "speaker": "luming",
          "text": "你昨夜画了谁？"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "speaker": "folding_artisan",
          "text": "我只画我看见的。至于他们是否还站在这里，那是纸的礼仪。"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "text": "白纸边缘轻轻抖动，像海岸线被看不见的潮水啃食。"
        }
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "T1_02_choice_1",
          "text": "盯住纸的边缘：它像在吞空间",
          "target": "T1_05",
          "effects": [
            {
              "type": "inc",
              "key": "clue_flatten",
              "by": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "inc",
              "key": "science",
              "by": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "T1_02_choice_2",
          "text": "抢走黑石板",
          "target": "T1_04",
          "effects": [
            {
              "type": "inc",
              "key": "risk",
              "by": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "inc",
              "key": "heat",
              "by": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "T1_02_choice_3",
          "text": "假装赞美他的技艺，拖延时间",
          "target": "T1_03",
          "effects": [
            {
              "type": "inc",
              "key": "trust",
              "by": 1
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "T1_03",
      "title": "三十九只无声铃",
      "scene": {
        "background": "bg_t1_03",
        "music": "BGM_04_archive",
        "transition": "fade"
      },
      "steps": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "speaker": "huaiyi",
          "text": "失踪的人没有血迹，没有脚印。连别人对他们的记忆都像被压薄了。"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "speaker": "luming",
          "text": "只有画像还记得他们？"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "speaker": "huaiyi",
          "text": "不。画像不是记得，画像是在占有。"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "text": "你在空钩下发现一小片亮粉，薄得像从世界表面刮下来的霜。"
        }
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "T1_03_choice_1",
          "text": "保存亮粉样本",
          "target": "T1_05",
          "effects": [
            {
              "type": "inc",
              "key": "clue_flatten",
              "by": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "inc",
              "key": "science",
              "by": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "T1_03_choice_2",
          "text": "追问砾亲王为何邀请折页匠",
          "target": "T1_06",
          "effects": [
            {
              "type": "inc",
              "key": "politics",
              "by": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "T1_03_choice_3",
          "text": "让槐姨带平民离宫",
          "target": "T1_07",
          "effects": [
            {
              "type": "inc",
              "key": "trust",
              "by": 1
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "T1_04",
      "title": "封锁失败",
      "scene": {
        "background": "bg_t1_04",
        "music": "BGM_05_alarm",
        "transition": "fade"
      },
      "steps": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "text": "卫队冲进画室时，折页匠没有躲。他只是翻了一页。"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "speaker": "guard",
          "text": "殿下，我们——"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "text": "声音从立体变成薄薄一层，贴在墙上，像被雨水浸开的墨。"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "speaker": "monitor_voice",
          "text": "警告：故事内暴力指数上升。请保持寓言形态。"
        }
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "T1_04_choice_1",
          "text": "承认硬闯会触发灾害，转为观察机制",
          "target": "T1_05",
          "effects": [
            {
              "type": "inc",
              "key": "clue_flatten",
              "by": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "inc",
              "key": "risk",
              "by": -1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "T1_04_choice_2",
          "text": "继续派人夺取石板",
          "target": "chapter1.censored",
          "effects": [
            {
              "type": "inc",
              "key": "heat",
              "by": 2
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "T1_04_choice_3",
          "text": "撤退，寻找旧匠人",
          "target": "T1_07",
          "effects": [
            {
              "type": "inc",
              "key": "trust",
              "by": 1
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "T1_05",
      "title": "折叠不是绘画",
      "scene": {
        "background": "bg_t1_05",
        "music": "BGM_06_decode_soft",
        "transition": "fade"
      },
      "steps": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "speaker": "luming",
          "text": "他不是把人画进纸里。他是在把人的世界折成纸。"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "speaker": "sailor",
          "text": "北陆白城的匠人都这样说：能被看见的东西，终有一天会被做成平面。"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "speaker": "huaiyi",
          "text": "那要怎么不被看见？"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "text": "没有人回答。只有远处黑伞旋转的影子，在墙上像一枚缓慢的钟。"
        }
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "T1_05_choice_1",
          "text": "追踪黑伞来源",
          "target": "T1_07",
          "effects": [
            {
              "type": "inc",
              "key": "clue_umbrella",
              "by": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "T1_05_choice_2",
          "text": "询问风帆卫士关于北陆白城",
          "target": "T1_06",
          "effects": [
            {
              "type": "inc",
              "key": "worlds",
              "by": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "T1_05_choice_3",
          "text": "把‘被看见’标记为危险条件",
          "target": "T1_08",
          "effects": [
            {
              "type": "inc",
              "key": "clue_flatten",
              "by": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "inc",
              "key": "science",
              "by": 1
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "T1_06",
      "title": "世界不止一座岛",
      "scene": {
        "background": "bg_t1_06",
        "music": "BGM_07_world_map",
        "transition": "fade"
      },
      "steps": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "speaker": "sailor",
          "text": "殿下，拾声王国的海图只画到灯塔。灯塔外还有岛，岛外还有大陆，大陆外还有从不点灯的港。"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "speaker": "luming",
          "text": "那北陆为什么来我们这里？"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "speaker": "sailor",
          "text": "也许是交易，也许是试验，也许只是因为我们亮着。"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "text": "‘亮着’二字落在地图上，像一枚坐标。"
        }
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "T1_06_choice_1",
          "text": "记录：暴露位置本身即危险",
          "target": "T1_08",
          "effects": [
            {
              "type": "inc",
              "key": "clue_coordinate",
              "by": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "inc",
              "key": "science",
              "by": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "T1_06_choice_2",
          "text": "质疑风帆卫士是否另有目的",
          "target": "T1_09",
          "effects": [
            {
              "type": "inc",
              "key": "trust",
              "by": -1
            },
            {
              "type": "inc",
              "key": "risk",
              "by": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "T1_06_choice_3",
          "text": "让他带你寻找黑伞旧主",
          "target": "T1_07",
          "effects": [
            {
              "type": "inc",
              "key": "trust",
              "by": 1
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "T1_07",
      "title": "旋转黑伞",
      "scene": {
        "background": "bg_t1_07",
        "music": "BGM_08_black_umbrella",
        "transition": "fade"
      },
      "steps": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "speaker": "umbrella_master",
          "text": "别让伞停。停了，纸会想起我。"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "speaker": "luming",
          "text": "你也会被折进去？"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "speaker": "umbrella_master",
          "text": "我已经被折了一半。旋转只是让另一半暂时忘记该往哪里倒。"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "text": "伞骨每转一圈，周围烛火就暗一分，仿佛光走得越来越慢。"
        }
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "T1_07_choice_1",
          "text": "记录：黑伞通过降低光与信息传播保护局部",
          "target": "T1_08",
          "effects": [
            {
              "type": "inc",
              "key": "clue_slowlight",
              "by": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "inc",
              "key": "science",
              "by": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "T1_07_choice_2",
          "text": "问他如何击败折页匠",
          "target": "T1_09",
          "effects": [
            {
              "type": "inc",
              "key": "risk",
              "by": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "T1_07_choice_3",
          "text": "接过黑伞，准备撤离",
          "target": "T1_10",
          "effects": [
            {
              "type": "inc",
              "key": "clue_slowlight",
              "by": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "inc",
              "key": "trust",
              "by": 1
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "T1_08",
      "title": "童话中的第一条公式",
      "scene": {
        "background": "bg_t1_08",
        "music": "BGM_06_decode_soft",
        "transition": "fade"
      },
      "steps": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "speaker": "decoder",
          "text": "画页不是画；黑伞不是伞。一个代表空间被压成平面，一个代表局部光速被人为降低。"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "speaker": "chengan",
          "text": "他说得这么明显，为什么监察还允许？"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "speaker": "monitor_voice",
          "text": "伞、纸、铃、海：均为童话词汇。通信继续。"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "text": "你明白了：故事不是藏得越深越安全，而是要藏在审查者不相信的地方。"
        }
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "T1_08_choice_1",
          "text": "继续回到钟楼，听完黑伞的限制",
          "target": "T1_09",
          "effects": [
            {
              "type": "inc",
              "key": "science",
              "by": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "T1_08_choice_2",
          "text": "先标记为‘防御方案’",
          "target": "T1_10",
          "effects": [
            {
              "type": "inc",
              "key": "clue_slowlight",
              "by": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "T1_08_choice_3",
          "text": "把这个解释说得更直白",
          "target": "chapter1.censored",
          "effects": [
            {
              "type": "inc",
              "key": "heat",
              "by": 2
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "T1_09",
      "title": "伞不能太快，也不能太慢",
      "scene": {
        "background": "bg_t1_09",
        "music": "BGM_08_black_umbrella",
        "transition": "fade"
      },
      "steps": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "speaker": "umbrella_master",
          "text": "伞快了，伞下的人会永远听不见外面的钟。伞慢了，外面的纸会先听见你。"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "speaker": "luming",
          "text": "所以它既是盾，也是牢。"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "speaker": "umbrella_master",
          "text": "每一种幸存都有价格。别让价格伪装成胜利。"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "text": "他把伞柄交给你。自己的身形随即薄成一片透明的影。"
        }
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "T1_09_choice_1",
          "text": "带伞离开王宫",
          "target": "T1_10",
          "effects": [
            {
              "type": "inc",
              "key": "clue_slowlight",
              "by": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "inc",
              "key": "trust",
              "by": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "T1_09_choice_2",
          "text": "追击折页匠，验证伞的效果",
          "target": "T1_11",
          "effects": [
            {
              "type": "inc",
              "key": "risk",
              "by": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "inc",
              "key": "clue_flatten",
              "by": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "T1_09_choice_3",
          "text": "留在钟楼继续问代价",
          "target": "T1_11",
          "effects": [
            {
              "type": "inc",
              "key": "science",
              "by": 1
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "T1_10",
      "title": "离宫",
      "scene": {
        "background": "bg_t1_10",
        "music": "BGM_09_escape_low",
        "transition": "fade"
      },
      "steps": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "speaker": "prince_li",
          "text": "姐姐，你带着一把破伞就想继承王国？"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "speaker": "luming",
          "text": "我不是去继承王国。我要先确认它还能不能被继承。"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "text": "雪阶下方，整座王宫的侧影正在变薄，像有人从远处合上一册巨书。"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "speaker": "sailor",
          "text": "去海边。若还有答案，它不会在宫墙里。"
        }
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "T1_10_choice_1",
          "text": "立刻前往海边",
          "target": "chapter1.to_chapter2",
          "effects": [
            {
              "type": "inc",
              "key": "act1_done",
              "by": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "T1_10_choice_2",
          "text": "回头看最后一眼，确认画页扩散速度",
          "target": "T1_11",
          "effects": [
            {
              "type": "inc",
              "key": "clue_flatten",
              "by": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "inc",
              "key": "science",
              "by": 1
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "T1_11",
      "title": "一掌宽的世界",
      "scene": {
        "background": "bg_t1_11",
        "music": "BGM_10_cosmic_fear",
        "transition": "fade"
      },
      "steps": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "speaker": "huaiyi",
          "text": "它没有一下子吞掉城。它在长大。"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "speaker": "sailor",
          "text": "灾害有速度，就意味着还有逃离窗口。"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "speaker": "luming",
          "text": "一掌宽，足够埋葬一个房间；一夜，足够埋葬一个王国。"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "text": "你记住这句童话式的测量。"
        }
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "T1_11_choice_1",
          "text": "把‘扩散速度’标记为关键警告",
